data.description: Welcome to this charming home in Fig Garden! This 3/2 gem features a secluded media room, fresh interior paint, newer central HVAC, water heater, and dual pane windows. Enjoy features such as a tile roof, bay window, dishwasher, and built-in gas fireplace. With top-rated schools, great dining, shopping, and easy freeway access nearby, this home offers convenience and comfort. Schedule a showing today and make it yours!
